%% Sequence Diagram -- BACKLOG.md Creation During Install (REQ-0014)

sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as bin/isdlc.js init
    participant Installer as lib/installer.js install()
    participant FS as fs-helpers
    participant Logger as logger

    Note over CLI,Logger: ... Steps 1-6 complete ...

    CLI->>Installer: install(projectRoot, options)

    Note over Installer: CLAUDE.md creation block (existing)

    Installer->>FS: exists(projectRoot + '/BACKLOG.md')

    alt BACKLOG.md exists
        FS-->>Installer: true
        Installer->>Logger: info('BACKLOG.md already exists -- skipping')
    else BACKLOG.md does not exist
        FS-->>Installer: false

        alt dryRun is true
            Installer->>Logger: success('Created BACKLOG.md')
            Note over Installer: No file written (dry-run)
        else dryRun is false
            Installer->>Installer: generateBacklogMd()
            Installer->>FS: writeFile(backlogPath, content)
            FS-->>Installer: ok
            Installer->>Logger: success('Created BACKLOG.md')
        end
    end

    Note over Installer: Step 7: Generate state.json
